Text: If you were looking and hoping for a high quality release, too bad, this is again re-encoded low quality crap.

Yes, I have (I never comment on quality without listening) and I can hear its low quality effects, but I know a lot of people can't disscern 128kbps (or even lower) from original/lossless. If you're one of those people, that's good for you and I hope you enjoy it :) If you aren't, I suggest waiting a day or two until a quality release shows up.
Those who can't wait, get it from the Russians...
